_header: I seek about this world unstable
_description: William Dunbar, ‘Of the changes of life’ — four 5-line stanzas

CULLl510.First Lines:
I Seik about þis warld vnstabellTo seile and sentances
                    conveneabill…
CULLl510.Last Lines:
…nixt eftir joy ay cumes sorowSo is þis world and ay hes
                    ben
